The paper deals with text extraction and recognition from natural scene images, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper focuses on extracting regional languages, which falls under natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of deep learning techniques for text recognition and language translation also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves GPS coordinates and location-based information, which could be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the use of neural networks and deep learning models suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG).
